          "Evaluate the exact special angles. $n=4$: $\\csc45^{\\circ}=\\sqrt2$, so $R=(\\sqrt2-1)r$ ŌĆö equality, so (A) fails. $n=12$: $\\csc15^{\\circ}=\\sqrt6+\\sqrt2$, so $\\dfrac{R}{r}=\\sqrt6+\\sqrt2-1\\approx2.864$.",
